{"tid":290900,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"摯 我深愛的大美人","createTime":"2017-06-20T06:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T23:07:27.000Z","uid":82917,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14f630a64d9f43d58a927548c846eb6d7538dff5","tid":290900,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T06:45:49.000Z","msg":"Dearest Queen M,<br />\n<br />\n星星守護著月亮，所以月亮睡的安詳，<br />\n溫暖守護著春天，所以春天笑得燦爛。<br />\n我會守護著妳！所以希望妳一輩子都快快樂樂。<br />\n老天讓妳在這一天降生，為的就是讓我行走的路上不孤單！今天是妳生日，感謝這個日子。<br />\n妳的生日我將永生謹記，妳的生日我將祝福到底！<br />\n我知道，我這樣做，對於妳來說是侮辱妳的智慧，是戇居的！<br />\n但，我願意成為妳唯一的痴心情長劍！<br />\n對妳始終如一！至死不渝！<br />\n恭喜妳！生日快快樂樂！永遠美麗！幸福快樂！<br />\n我對大美人的情不會變！<br />\n我的心裡都是愛！今生今世不離不棄！<br />\n我愛妳！李嘉欣！！！麼麼噠～～～～<br />\nTHE ONE，AND ONLY<br />\n<br />\n祝 生日快樂。❤️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWith love,<br />\n妳的榮譽粉絲 &mdash; 宇宙第一美人"},{"pid":"bae614930fadf8dec29a47e4628516bc10336f34","tid":290900,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T06:58:59.000Z","msg":"點解。。點解上傳圖片失敗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然妳已貴爲人妻<br />\n但妳在我心中仍是當年那個想盡辦法捧紅好朋友的那個純真女孩 <br />\n不求回報 姊妹情深 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n若我有著嘉欣這般為朋友着想的朋友 我定必赴湯蹈火 在所不惜"},{"pid":"ebce685da7b3756ae5cd9da16efede6e54d41930","tid":290900,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T07:00:19.000Z","msg":"很想和大家分享我珍藏已久的 大美人 李嘉欣 獨照啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843b1f47d00bc0e90fb2e9f9dfbbefa806b60dcd","tid":290900,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T07:02:09.000Z","msg":"人地牛一大日子都負皮<br />\n你地呢d平民真係不識好歹<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我願代替他們為大美人獻上最真誠的祝福❤️"},{"pid":"4e7ee9d52cc1d3892f3626a6c7d905ee0f1754c6","tid":290900,"uid":62517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T07:02:31.000Z","msg":"乜撚野叫麼麼噠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd8cc9bd8edc19791874ca6a09afacb47b5badf","tid":290900,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T07:03:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜撚野叫麼麼噠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n眼底盡是愛意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226192d7682d10bf6b1dad5cd478e15f5dfe2adb","tid":290900,"uid":70198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T07:04:47.000Z","msg":"痴線"},{"pid":"6ee8392cdb95ec210663cb5fde158d354899799a","tid":290900,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T07:05:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴線</blockquote><br />\n你懂什麼是愛啊！？"},{"pid":"90cac76e507c73e494e25cdf1ffcebae82e992dd","tid":290900,"uid":21166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:25:47.000Z","msg":"夠鐘食藥啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b34b319380dc760e66e4085fb207af4b5870914","tid":290900,"uid":82917,"like":0,"disl